---
import SlideCarousel from "../components/SlideCarousel.astro";
import PageLayout from "../layouts/PageLayout.astro";
---

<style>
	h2 {
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		line-height: 1.125;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		letter-spacing: -0.01em;
		padding-top: 1.25rem;
	}

	.hero span {
		font-weight: normal;
	}

	p {
		max-width: 50ch;
	}

	ul {
		list-style: disc;
		margin-left: 1.375rem;
	}

	.three-photos {
		padding-block: 1rem;
		display: grid;
		gap: 1rem;

		@media (width >= 32rem) {
			grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		}
	}

	h3 {
		font-family: "Inter", sans-serif, system-ui;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 350;
		letter-spacing: 0.01em;
		padding-top: 1rem;
	}

	h4 {
		font-weight: bold;
		font-size: 1.625rem;
	}
</style>

<PageLayout>
	<h2 class="hero">
		Bohdan Yaroslavtsev
		<span>aka <i>@reoseah</i> online</span>
	</h2>

	<p>
		Human, programmer, web developer, hobby game modder and developer, and
		some other things.
	</p>

	<div>
		<b>Contents</b>
		<ul>
			<li>
				<a href="#something-resembling-portfolio"
					>Something resembling portfolio</a
				>
			</li>
			<li>
				<a href="#">More things to come</a>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</div>

	<section class="three-photos">
		<img src="/assets/photo-1.jpg" alt="selfie with a colored lens" />
		<img src="/assets/photo-2.jpg" alt="selfie through a piece of cloth" />
		<img src="/assets/photo-3.jpg" alt="selfie with a piece of plastic" />
	</section>

	<h2 id="something-resembling-portfolio">Something resembling portfolio</h2>

	<p>
		Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Rem dicta,
		fugit obcaecati consequuntur similique architecto necessitatibus ullam
		doloremque illum eum, eos sapiente fugiat. Sequi inventore repellat quo
		nobis sunt excepturi.
	</p>

	<h3>Escuelas Taller "Gijón Acompaña"</h3>

	<h4>Version for project's "website"</h4>
	<p>
		The first this we did <s>in absence of something more useful</s> were designs
		for a website for the project itself, then voted on which one we liked. I
		should have voted for myself, in retrospective.
	</p>

	<SlideCarousel
		images={[
			{
				src: "/assets/et23 desktop header.webp",
				alt: "screenshot of the site on desktop screen",
			},
			{
				src: "/assets/et23 mobile header.webp",
				alt: "screenshot of the site on mobile screen",
			},
			{
				src: "/assets/et23 v0.png",
				alt: "screenshot of the very early version of the site",
				description:
					"A very early version. I viewed too much media saying neo-brutalism was going to be a trend in 2023",
			},
		]}
	/>
</PageLayout>
